<title>Keyboard shortcuts</title>

<p>The following keyboard shortcuts are available:</p>

<terms>
    <item>
        <title><keyseq><key>Crtl</key><key>Z</key></keyseq></title>
        <p>Undo the last undoable action.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title><keyseq><key>Crtl</key><key>Y</key></keyseq></title>
        <p>Redo the last undone action.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title><keyseq><key>Crtl</key><key>Q</key></keyseq></title>
        <p>Quit the application.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title><keyseq><key>F1</key></keyseq></title>
        <p>Display user help.</p>
    </item>
</terms>

